<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Account Password Reset - {{nooriescornerApp.name}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .logo img {
            max-width: 300px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="logo">
        <img src="{{nooriescornerApp.logo}}" alt="Logo">
    </div>
    <h3>Hi {{username}},</h3>
    <p>We received a request to reset your password for your Noorie's Corner account.</p>
    <p>Please click the link below to reset your password:</p>
    <p><a href="{{resetLink}}">Reset Password</a></p>
    <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your current password will remain unchanged.
    </p>
    <p>For security purposes, this link will expire in 60 minutes.</p>
    <p>If you need any assistance or have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact our support team at
        <a href="mailto:{{nooriescornerApp.email}}">{{nooriescornerApp.email}}</a>.
    </p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>{{nooriescornerApp.name}} Team</p>
</body>

</html>